<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>許毓庭的個人主頁</title>
    <style>
        /* 基本樣式設定 */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif, "Microsoft JhengHei";
            background-color: #f4f7f6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* 卡片容器 */
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* 大頭貼圖示 */
        .profile-img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .info-grid {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 1rem;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            display: flex;
        }

        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4a90e2;
            width: 85px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .content {
            color: #555;
        }

        /* 未來目標區塊 */
        .goal {
            background-color: #eef6ff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #4a90e2;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #aaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="profile-img">毓庭</div>
    <h1>許毓庭</h1>
    <p style="color: #7f8c8d; margin-top: 0;">國立金門大學 · 資工系</p>

    <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-item">
            <span class="label">年齡：</span>
            <span class="content">18 歲</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
            <span class="label">家鄉：</span>
            <span class="content">嘉義</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
            <span class="label">學校：</span>
            <span class="content">金門大學</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
            <span class="label">科系：</span>
            <span class="content">資訊工程學系</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3 style="text-align: left; color: #2c3e50;">未來目標</h3>
    <div class="goal">
        未來希望能在資工領域發展，也希望能不斷提升自己，掌握最新的技術與挑戰。
    </div>

    <footer>
        © 2024 許毓庭 Personal Page
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>



